  <?dbhtml filename="hdf5.html"?>

  <title>HDF5-&hdf5-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      HDF5 is a data model, library, and file format for storing and managing
      data. It supports an unlimited variety of datatypes, and is designed for
      flexible and efficient I/O and for high volume and complex data. This
      package includes tools for managing, manipulating, viewing, and analyzing
      data in the HDF5 format.
    </para>

